{
  "name": "teams_update-discussion-legacy",
  "description": "**Deprecation Notice:** This endpoint route is deprecated and will be removed from the Teams API. We recommend migrating your existing code to use the new [Update a discussion](https://docs.github.com/enterprise-server@2.21/rest/reference/teams#update-a-discussion) endpoint.\n\nEdits the title and body text of a discussion post. Only the parameters you provide are updated. OAuth access tokens require the `write:discussion` [scope](https://docs.github.com/enterprise-server@2.21/apps/building-oauth-apps/understanding-scopes-for-oauth-apps/).",
  "parameters": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "team_id": {
        "type": "integer"
      },
      "discussion_number": {
        "type": "integer"
      },
      "body": {
        "properties": {
          "body": {
            "description": "The discussion post's body text.",
            "type": "string"
          },
          "title": {
            "description": "The discussion post's title.",
            "type": "string"
          }
        },
        "type": "object"
      }
    },
    "required": [
      "team_id",
      "discussion_number"
    ]
  },
  "handler": "http",
  "request": {
    "method": "PATCH",
    "url": {
      "$uri": "http://HOSTNAME/api/v3/teams/{team_id}/discussions/{discussion_number}"
    },
    "body": {
      "$": "body",
      "encode": "json"
    }
  },
  "responses": {
    "200": {
      "$encode": "markdown",
      "$block": [
        {
          "$h1": "Team Discussion"
        },
        "A team discussion is a persistent record of a free-form conversation within a team.",
        "**Key properties:**",
        {
          "$ul": [
            [
              "**author**: Simple User",
              {
                "$ul": [
                  "**avatar_url**",
                  "**email**",
                  "**events_url**",
                  "**followers_url**",
                  "**following_url**",
                  "**gists_url**",
                  "**gravatar_id**",
                  "**html_url**",
                  "**id**",
                  "**login**",
                  "**name**",
                  "**node_id**",
                  "**organizations_url**",
                  "**received_events_url**",
                  "**repos_url**",
                  "**site_admin**",
                  "**starred_at**",
                  "**starred_url**",
                  "**subscriptions_url**",
                  "**type**",
                  "**url**"
                ]
              }
            ],
            "**body**: The main text of the discussion.",
            "**body_html**",
            "**body_version**: The current version of the body content. If provided, this update operation will be rejected if the given version does not match the latest version on the server.",
            "**comments_count**",
            "**comments_url**",
            "**created_at**",
            "**html_url**",
            "**last_edited_at**",
            "**node_id**",
            "**number**: The unique sequence number of a team discussion.",
            "**pinned**: Whether or not this discussion should be pinned for easy retrieval.",
            "**private**: Whether or not this discussion should be restricted to team members and organization administrators.",
            [
              "**reactions**",
              {
                "$ul": [
                  "**+1**",
                  "**-1**",
                  "**confused**",
                  "**eyes**",
                  "**heart**",
                  "**hooray**",
                  "**laugh**",
                  "**rocket**",
                  "**total_count**",
                  "**url**"
                ]
              }
            ],
            "**team_url**",
            "**title**: The title of the discussion.",
            "**updated_at**",
            "**url**"
          ]
        },
        {
          "$lang": "json",
          "$code": {
            "$encode": "json",
            "$indent": true,
            "$content": {
              "$": "$.body"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}
